Class PrincipalLoginHistoryItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.users.model.PrincipalLoginHistoryItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    @Entity
public class PrincipalLoginHistoryItem
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<PrincipalLoginHistoryItem>, java.io.Serializable
    Represents a time when the Principal authenticated and also the time that the authentication session ended.

    Ken Logan (ken@i2rd.com)
